{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "诺斯通（夏日Ver.） 第5话 传递幸福的故事",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "（绘本总算是完成了。\\n剩下的就是……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "（得先自报家门才行……\\n笔谈应该没问题吧……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“初次见面，\\n我是绘本作家，名叫诺斯通。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "“绘本作家找我有什么事？”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“我有一本绘本想送给您，\\n特此来访。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "“送我绘本？什么绘本？”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“是一本名为《海之歌》的绘本。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "啊！拜托您了！\\n请务必看一次！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“这是专门为了您\\n而创作的绘本。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“我知道您曾经\\n遭遇了不幸的海难，\\n还因此导致失聪。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“现实非常残酷，\\n我也很理解您绝望的心情。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“正因如此，\\n我希望能驱散您的绝望。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“哪怕只有一次也好，\\n请您看看这本绘本。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "“我知道了。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "谢谢您！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "（这、这绘本……难道！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "那片海里，有一位美丽的歌姬。\\n在某个暴风雨降临之日，\\n歌姬不幸与她\\n重要的朋友分开了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_210054_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "孤零零的歌姬\\n在孤独的海中不断歌唱着。\\n饱含着对朋友的思念，\\n在美丽而深沉的海底独自吟唱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "这之后过了多久呢？\\n有一天，歌姬受魔法之力的指引\\n来到了海面之上的世界。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_sty_bg_0079_100"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "美丽的群星久违地映入眼帘，\\n歌姬摇荡在银色的波涛中，\\n下定了决心。\\n\\n“我要去见你。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "“只要你还在等待，\\n只要你露出笑容，\\n我就会一直为你歌唱。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "歌姬在广阔无边的海里遨游。\\n就算要从无数繁星中寻找，\\n她也要找到她的朋友。\\n即使天空黯淡，\\n即使阴雨连绵。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "“只要你还在等待。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "呜呜……呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“这本绘本，是想象着\\n塞壬的歌声画成的。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“我希望能把她的歌声\\n带给你。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“塞壬，你出来吧。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120137_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "保罗……终于，又见到你了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "啊……啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "我好想你啊。\\n一直，一直都……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "呜呜……呜呜！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "呜呜…呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "我一直都想见你，\\n想当面向你道歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "都怪我，让你受苦了，\\n抱歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "不，哪里，\\n没那回事！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "要是我先去找你就好了……\\n每当我看到大海，\\n就会想起你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "不能再听到你的歌声\\n让我无法忍耐……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "所以才一直待在\\n远离海边的家里\\n闭门不出。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "都怪我太懦弱，\\n就算大家那么过分地指责你，\\n我也无言以对……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "没关系，都过去了。\\n我还能再次见到你，\\n就已经很开心了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "我是来让你露出笑容的哦☆\\n所以笑一个吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "你的歌声……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120137_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "依然是那么美妙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "“虽然我现在听不到了，\\n但你的歌声还萦绕在耳边。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "“是这本绘本让我回想起来这歌声。\\n谢谢你带来这么出色的作品。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120137_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "我也非常感谢你☆\\n真的帮我实现了梦想……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "哪里，我只是画了一本绘本而已。\\n真正厉害的是你的歌声。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120137_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "哪里的话！\\n我现在就像绘本里的公主那样\\n感到非常幸福！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120137_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "这都多亏你对我施了\\n幸福的魔法☆",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "……\\n那就好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "“塞壬，\\n你能为我唱首歌吗？”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "保罗",
            "context": "“不管是以前还是现在，\\n我都最喜欢你的歌声和笑容了。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120137_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "没问题！\\n用欢乐的歌曲\\n把气氛炒热吧☆",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120137_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞壬",
            "context": "♪",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "（我给她施了\\n幸福的魔法……吗……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "（现实的确很残酷。\\n无情的悲剧\\n会令人绝望地袭来。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "（但是，悲剧过后\\n我们还可以描绘幸福的故事，\\n无论是幻想还是现实。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "（我要向他人传达这一点。\\n虽然我无法像尤蒂尔那样\\n成为希望本身。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "（但我能用幻想的力量\\n和画笔去创作绘本。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110066_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺斯通",
            "context": "“海之公主与王子，\\n幸福地相视而笑——\\n可喜可贺。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}